//UFSDCLNP PROC
//*
//* UFSDCLNP - Emergency UFSD Cleanup
//*
//* Deregisters the UFSD SSCT, unloads the SSI router from CSA,
//* and frees all CSA pools (requests, buffers, trace, anchor).
//* Run this after an UFSD abend before restarting UFSD.
//*
//* As STC:       /S UFSDCLNP
//* As batch:     Submit the UFSDCLNP JCL from SAMPLIB
//*
//* Safe to run when UFSD is not registered — reports
//* "nothing to do" and exits RC=0.
//*
//CLEANUP  EXEC PGM=UFSDCLNP
//STEPLIB  DD  DISP=SHR,DSN=UFSD.LINKLIB
